/*----------------------------------------------------------*\
  constant/propertyManifest -- property-record OWNERSHIP registry
  (context: BRINE).  Written by bin/choupo-import from the Choupo-2607 catalogue
  release; the manifest is the authority on which files under
  constant/ the importer owns.  A file it does NOT claim is
  authored and untouchable; a claimed file it verifies by sha256.
  `sealed true;` FORBIDS the runtime every catalogue fallback --
  the case runs exclusively from its own constant/ records.
  claim types:  imported = installed + hash-verified copy;
                adopted  = authored record explicitly adopted at
                           import time (never installed, never
                           hash-enforced, never removed);
                merged   = standards base with a partial by-name
                           overlay applied top-level, materialised
                           at import time (base + overlay hashes
                           both recorded; durable like adopted).
\*----------------------------------------------------------*/

